INNER JOIN [PurchaseOrders] AS [p0] ON [p].[PurchaseOrderId] = [p0].[PurchaseOrderId]
INNER JOIN [Suppliers] AS [s] ON [p0].[SupplierId] = [s].[SupplierId]
WHERE [p].[PurchaseOrderId] = @__id_0

(@p22, @p23, @p24, @p25, @p26, @p27, @p28, @p29, @p30, @p31, @p32, 2)) AS i ([CreateBy], [CreateDate], [DeleteBy], [DeleteDate], [DeleteFlag], [PurchaseOrderId], [Quantity], [UnitPrice], [UpdateBy], [UpdateDate], [VehicleId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([CreateBy], [CreateDate], [DeleteBy], [DeleteDate], [DeleteFlag], [PurchaseOrderId], [Quantity], [UnitPrice], [UpdateBy], [UpdateDate], [VehicleId])
VALUES (i.[CreateBy], i.[CreateDate], i.[DeleteBy], i.[DeleteDate], i.[DeleteFlag], i.[PurchaseOrderId], i.[Quantity], i.[UnitPrice], i.[UpdateBy], i.[UpdateDate], i.[VehicleId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[PurchaseOrderDetailId], i._Position;
UPDATE [PurchaseOrders] SET [CreateBy] = @p33, [CreateDate] = @p34, [DeleteBy] = @p35, [DeleteDate] = @p36, [DeleteFlag] = @p37, [OrderDate] = @p38, [SupplierId] = @p39, [TotalAmount] = @p40, [UpdateBy] = @p41, [UpdateDate] = @p42
OUTPUT 1
WHERE [PurchaseOrderId] = @p43;
MERGE [StockHistory] USING (
VALUES (@p44, @p45, @p46, @p47, @p48, 0),
(@p49, @p50, @p51, @p52, @p53, 1),
(@p54, @p55, @p56, @p57, @p58, 2)) AS i ([ChangeDate], [ChangeType], [Quantity], [UserId], [VehicleId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([ChangeDate], [ChangeType], [Quantity], [UserId], [VehicleId])
VALUES (i.[ChangeDate], i.[ChangeType], i.[Quantity], i.[UserId], i.[VehicleId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[StockHistoryId], i._Position;
